      "versionNonce": 1354149843,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780372267628,
      "link": null,
      "text": "• Backend Engine: FastAPI (Python 3.13) + Uvicorn server\n• Orchestration: LangChain (create_deep_agent)\n• Vector Graph Database: Neo4j (APOC & Graph Data Science plugins)\n• Local LLM Engine: Ollama (Models: qwen3.5:4b & qwen3.5:0.8b)\n• Local Embeddings: jina-embeddings-v2-base-en (8K context length)\n• Neural Reranker: HuggingFace Cross-Encoder (ms-marco-MiniLM-L-6-v2)\n• Frontend Web Application: Streamlit (Multi-page chat UI)\n• Service Isolation: Docker Compose orchestration",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "55c5d5a8-ff43-45ab-9a9c-4afa12ac4252",
      "originalText": "• Backend Engine: FastAPI (Python 3.13) + Uvicorn server\n• Orchestration: LangChain (create_deep_agent)\n• Vector Graph Database: Neo4j (APOC & Graph Data Science plugins)\n• Local LLM Engine: Ollama (Models: qwen3.5:4b & qwen3.5:0.8b)\n• Local Embeddings: jina-embeddings-v2-base-en (8K context length)\n• Neural Reranker: HuggingFace Cross-Encoder (ms-marco-MiniLM-L-6-v2)\n• Frontend Web Application: Streamlit (Multi-page chat UI)\n• Service Isolation: Docker Compose orchestration",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b0O",
      "frameId": null,
      "locked": false
    },
