      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780372267628,
      "link": null,
      "text": "• Privacy First: All LLM reasoning & vector operations execute locally.\n• Hybrid GraphRAG Retrieval: Combines vector index search with Cypher\n  traversals to fetch complete context chains (tags + parent links).\n• SSE Streaming Engine: High performance real-time token-by-token client push.\n• Visible Thought Process: Expandable UI containers showing step-by-step reasoning.\n• Session Repair Service: Startup database health check restoring session nodes.\n• Ingestion Panel: Search-import developer dashboard fetching StackExchange items.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "2ff95f24-38b2-4583-af73-7b9b1d6e9e6a",
      "originalText": "• Privacy First: All LLM reasoning & vector operations execute locally.\n• Hybrid GraphRAG Retrieval: Combines vector index search with Cypher\n  traversals to fetch complete context chains (tags + parent links).\n• SSE Streaming Engine: High performance real-time token-by-token client push.\n• Visible Thought Process: Expandable UI containers showing step-by-step reasoning.\n• Session Repair Service: Startup database health check restoring session nodes.\n• Ingestion Panel: Search-import developer dashboard fetching StackExchange items.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b0S",
      "frameId": null,
      "locked": false
    },
