      "updated": 1780372267628,
      "link": null,
      "text": "🤖 Auto Retrieval Mode (Structured Graph Cypher)\n\n1. LLM generates a structured Cypher query based on database schema.\n2. Executes vector index lookups using the query embedding.\n3. Traverses graph paths to fetch adjacent Tag and User relationships.\n4. Feeds candidate documents through HF CrossEncoder Reranker.\n5. Forms a context block sorted by neural relevance.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "85a47200-b4cb-45f3-8bd7-2989105c4dd1",
      "originalText": "🤖 Auto Retrieval Mode (Structured Graph Cypher)\n\n1. LLM generates a structured Cypher query based on database schema.\n2. Executes vector index lookups using the query embedding.\n3. Traverses graph paths to fetch adjacent Tag and User relationships.\n4. Feeds candidate documents through HF CrossEncoder Reranker.\n5. Forms a context block sorted by neural relevance.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b0W",
      "frameId": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "4dc461e9-3722-4bd6-8cff-7e98e88f47a5",
