      "seed": 6175776,
      "version": 11,
      "versionNonce": 1330605043,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780372267628,
      "link": null,
      "text": "🔧 Custom Retrieval Mode (Unstructured Vector/BM25 Ensemble)\n\n1. Converts user input into vector embedding + keyword query string.\n2. Invokes similarity searches across 4 stores (User, Tag, Qn, Ans).\n3. EnsembleRetriever combines results dynamically using equal weighting.\n4. Sanitizes doc sizes, applies cross-encoder reranking.\n5. Selects top elements with highest similarity threshold.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "4dc461e9-3722-4bd6-8cff-7e98e88f47a5",
      "originalText": "🔧 Custom Retrieval Mode (Unstructured Vector/BM25 Ensemble)\n\n1. Converts user input into vector embedding + keyword query string.\n2. Invokes similarity searches across 4 stores (User, Tag, Qn, Ans).\n3. EnsembleRetriever combines results dynamically using equal weighting.\n4. Sanitizes doc sizes, applies cross-encoder reranking.\n5. Selects top elements with highest similarity threshold.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b0Y",
      "frameId": null,
      "locked": false
    }
